&none  &none        &kp F4  &kp F5  &kp F6  &kp F11    &kp PRINTSCREEN  &sk LEFT_SHIFT  &sk LCTRL  &sk LALT  &sk LEFT_GUI  &none
&none  &key_repeat  &kp F1  &kp F2  &kp F3  &kp F10    &kp CAPS         &kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp LCTRL  &kp LALT  &kp LEFT_GUI  &none
                            &none   &none   &none      &none            &none           &none
