&none  &sk LEFT_GUI  &sk LALT  &sk LCTRL  &sk LEFT_SHIFT  &none    &kp HOME      &kp LEFT    &kp DOWN    &kp RIGHT   &kp END             &none
&none  &kp LEFT_GUI  &kp LALT  &kp LCTRL  &kp LEFT_SHIFT  &none    &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp C_PREV  &kp C_PLAY  &kp C_NEXT  &kp K_CONTEXT_MENU  &none
                               &none      &none           &none    &none         &none       &none
